on-divider\" id=\"form-s6\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-num\">6</div>\n    <div class=\"section-title\">D√©membrement (art. 669-1)</div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"font-size: .85em; margin: 8px 0;\">Bar√®me fiscal usufruit/nue-propri√©t√© par √¢ge de l'usufruitier :</p>\n  <table class=\"compact-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>√Çge</th>\n        <th>Usufruit</th>\n        <th>Nue-propri√©t√©</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td>&lt; 21 ans</td><td>90%</td><td>10%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>21‚Äì30</td><td>80%</td><td>20%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>31‚Äì40</td><td>70%</td><td>30%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>41‚Äì50</td><td>60%</td><td>40%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>51‚Äì60</td><td>50%</td><td>50%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>61‚Äì70</td><td>40%</td><td>60%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>71‚Äì80</td><td>30%</td><td>70%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>81‚Äì90</td><td>20%</td><td>80%</td></tr>\n      <tr><td>&gt; 90</td><td>10%</td><td>90%</td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\" style=\"margin-top: 12px;\">\n    <h4>DTUS (art. 669-2)</h4>\n    <div class=\"f\">Droits temporaires = 23% PP par tranche 10 ans</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 7: Assurance Vie -->\n<div class=\"section section-divider\" id=\"form-s7\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-num\">7</div>\n    <div class=\"section-title\">Assurance Vie</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\">\n    <h4>Seuils exon√©ration (art. 990I)</h4>\n    <div class=\"note\">\n      <strong>Primes avant 70 ans :</strong> 152 500‚Ç¨/b√©n√©ficiaire exon√©r√©, puis 20%‚Üí31,25%<br>\n      <strong>Primes apr√®s 70 ans (art. 757B) :</strong> 30 500‚Ç¨ global exon√©r√©, droits succession au-del√†\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\">\n    <h4>Rachat &amp; Plus-values</h4>\n    <div class=\"f\">Rachat &gt;8 ans: abatt. 4 600‚Ç¨ (seul) / 9 200‚Ç¨ (couple)</div>\n    <div class=\"f\">Plus-value = Rachat √ó (Produits/Valeur contrat)</div>\n    <div class=\"f\">PFL: 7,5% (&lt; 150k) ou 12,8% (&gt; 150k)</div>\n    <div class=\"note\">Versements post-27/09/2017</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 8: Immobilier D√©fiscalisation -->\n<div class=\"section section-divider\" id=\"form-s8\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-num\">8</div>\n    <div class=\"section-title\">Immobilier D√©fiscalisation</div>\n  </div>\n  <table class=\"compact-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th style=\"font-size: .8em;\">Dispositif</th>\n        <th style=\"font-size: .8em;\">Type</th>\n        <th style=\"font-size: .8em;\">Taux/Montant</th>\n        <th style=\"font-size: .8em;\">Plafond</th>\n        <th style=\"font-size: .8em;\">Dur√©e</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>Pinel+</strong></td>\n        <td>R√©duction IR</td>\n        <td>10,5/15/17,5%</td>\n        <td>300k‚Ç¨</td>\n        <td>6/9/12 ans</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>Malraux</strong></td>\n        <td>R√©duction IR</td>\n        <td>22%/30%</td>\n        <td>400k‚Ç¨/4 ans</td>\n        <td>4 ans</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>M√©tiers H√©ritage</strong></td>\n        <td>D√©duction RG</td>\n        <td>100% travaux</td>\n        <td>Illimit√©</td>\n        <td>15 ans</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>D√©ficit foncier</strong></td>\n        <td>D√©duction RG</td>\n        <td>Charges‚àírevenus</td>\n        <td>10 700‚Ç¨/an</td>\n        <td>3 ans</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>LMNP micro</strong></td>\n        <td>Abattement</td>\n        <td>50%</td>\n        <td>77 700‚Ç¨ CA</td>\n        <td>‚Äî</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr style=\"font-size: .8em;\">\n        <td><strong>LMNP r√©el</strong></td>\n        <td>Charges+amort.</td>\n        <td>Sur BIC meubl√©</td>\n        <td>‚Äî</td>\n        <td>‚Äî</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 9: PER -->\n<div class=\"section section-divider\" id=\"form-s9\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-num\">9</div>\n    <div class=\"section-title\">PER (Plan d'√âpargne Retraite)</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\">\n    <h4>Plafonds d√©duction</h4>\n    <div class=\"f\">Salaried: 10% revenus N‚àí1 (min 10% PASS)</div>\n    <div class=\"f\" style=\"color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600;\">Min = 4 637‚Ç¨ | Max = 37 094‚Ç¨</div>\n    <div class=\"note\">TNS: plafond compl√©mentaire Madelin</div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\">\n    <h4>Sortie retraite</h4>\n    <div class=\"note\">\n      <strong>Capital :</strong> IR (versements) + PFU (gains)<br>\n      <strong>Rente (RVTO) :</strong> Abattement 40% (60‚Äì69 ans) ou 30% (&gt;70 ans)<br>\n      <strong>Report :</strong> 3 ans + mutualisation couple\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 10: R√©serve H√©r√©ditaire & Quotit√© Disponible -->\n<div class=\"section section-divider\" id=\"form-s10\">\n  <div class=\"section-header\">\n    <div class=\"section-num\">10</div>\n    <div class=\"section-title\">R√©serve H√©r√©ditaire &amp; Quotit√© Disponible</div>\n  </div>\n  <table class=\"compact-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Enfants</th>\n        <th>R√©serve</th>\n        <th>Quotit√© disponible</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr><td><strong>1 enfant</strong></td><td><strong>1/2</strong></td><td><strong>1/2</strong></td></tr>\n      <tr><td><strong>2 enfants</strong></td><td><strong>2/3</strong></td><td><strong>1/3</strong></td></tr>\n      <tr class=\"bold-row\"><td><strong>3+ enfants</strong></td><td><strong>3/4</strong></td><td><strong>1/4</strong></td></tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  <div class=\"formula-card\" style=\"margin-top: 12px;\">\n    <h4>Conjoint survivant</h4>\n    <div class=\"n